snippet.textDisplay: "When u down bad" it doesn't always mean nobody wants to be in your corner. It just means people stopped seeing the value in being around somebody who has no ambition because u just become a liability at that point.. Same reason why when people move up in life, they tend to "remove" people who are obviously there for the wrong reasons. I personally don't show "favoritism" but I see a lot of people commenting as if u need people in your corner while u down. Why worry about everybody else when u YOURSELF isn't together and everybody has their own issues and problems to deal with so why become part of someones problem? So there shouldn't be any reason why u worried about why nobody else is there cuz that's a good thing anyway. U shouldn't want nobody seeing u like that.. But that's my opinion 🤷🏽‍♂️.
